Package: edstr
Title: Extract Structured Data from Clinical Free Text
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R:
    person("Henry", "BOSTORRHUS", , "ju.diez@protonmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0001-3983-5713"))
Description: Extract structured variables from clinical text. Import
    tables from an 'Oracle' database, clean text with regex rules,
    tokenise and match user-defined concepts, and filter false
    positives. Results are exported as 'Excel', CSV, and RDS
    files for downstream analysis.
License: GPL (>= 3)
URL: https://github.com/hebstr/edstr
BugReports: https://github.com/hebstr/edstr/issues
SystemRequirements: Java (>= 8), Oracle Instant Client
Encoding: UTF-8
